subject: k1fluxxs
complexity_strategy: Placement/ratio of black and white squares

beauty_strategy: Intuition
most_beautiful:
I think I tended to think the beautiful ones were symmetrical. They reminded me of an old-fashioned quilt or cross-stitch, kind of a folk sort of beauty, which is ironic since they were computer-generated. 
I think I also thought ones were beautiful where I could "see" a scene/image in the design that wasn't there

subject: 4skc23wj

open_comments: For the questions on beauty and complexity, it could help if we saw references of the pictures we rated as 'most' complex/beautiful to even better explain why we chose what we chose.

subject: qra4neq0
